README.md
     5тЖТ# Tomli
     6тЖТ
     7тЖТ> A lil' TOML parser
     8тЖТ
     9тЖТ**Table of Contents** *generated with [mdformat-toc](https://github.com/hukkin/mdformat-toc)*
