tomllib.md
     1тЖТ# `tomllib` тАУ Tomli in the standard library
     2тЖТ
     3тЖТTomli was added to the Python standard library in Python 3.11.
     4тЖТ
     5тЖТRelevant links:
     6тЖТ
     7тЖТ- Python Issue Tracker: https://bugs.python.org/issue40059
     8тЖТ- Tomli issue tracker: https://github.com/hukkin/tomli/issues/141
     9тЖТ- Discussion on PyPA "blessing" a TOML parser and/or including one in the standard library: https://discuss.python.org/t/adopting-recommending-a-toml-parser/4068
    10тЖТ- Python Enhancement Proposal: https://peps.python.org/pep-0680
    11тЖТ- CPython pull request: https://github.com/python/cpython/pull/31498
    12тЖТ
    13тЖТ## Converting Tomli to tomllib
    14тЖТ
    15тЖТ### Sync status
    16тЖТ
    17тЖТ`tomllib` in CPython commit https://github.com/python/cpython/commit/deaf509e8fc6e0363bd6f26d52ad42f976ec42f2
    18тЖТmatches Tomli commit https://github.com/hukkin/tomli/commit/7e563eed5286b5d46b8290a9f56a86d955b23a9a
    19тЖТ
    20тЖТ### Steps to convert
    21тЖТ
    22тЖТ- Move everything in `tomli:src/tomli` to `cpython:Lib/tomllib`. Exclude `py.typed`.
    23тЖТ
    24тЖТ- Remove `__version__ = ...` line from `cpython:Lib/tomllib/__init__.py`
    25тЖТ
    26тЖТ- Move everything in `tomli:tests` to `cpython:Lib/test/test_tomllib`. Exclude the following test data dirs recursively:
    27тЖТ
    28тЖТ  - `tomli:tests/data/invalid/_external/`
    29тЖТ  - `tomli:tests/data/valid/_external/`
    30тЖТ
    31тЖТ- Create `cpython:Lib/test/test_tomllib/__main__.py`:
      тЖТтАж
